					  </p>
					</section>
				  </div>
				  <div class="col-3 col-12-narrower">
					<section>
					  <div class="icon-border">
						<span
						  style="padding-bottom: 10px"
						  class="icon solid featured icon-placeholder icon-supply"
						></span>
					  </div>
					  <header>
						<h3>Supply chain</h3>
					  </header>
					  <p>
						We take overall responsibility for product supply, complex and
						global deliveries: warehousing, packaging, and distribution.
					  </p>
					</section>
				  </div>
				  <div class="col-3 col-12-narrower">
					<section>
					  <div class="icon-border">
						<span
						  class="icon solid featured icon-placeholder icon-financial"
						></span>
					  </div>
					  <header>
						<h3>Financial fundament</h3>
					  </header>
					  <p>
						BIAB International has constantly received the highest credit
